/******************************************************************************************************
 * The following +ARGS can be passed for any UVM_TEST to control the tracker & its reports            *       
 * usage : make run_vsim DEBUG=1 PLUSARGS="+EN_TRACKER +GEN_REPORT"                                   *     
 * note  : these args apply to all the instances of the tracker                                       *       
 * Arg - "EN_TRACKER" : Enables the tracker to monitor the connected interface                        *     
 * Arg - "GEN_REPORT" : Enables the tracker to generate 2 files which are saved in sim/ by default    *
 *                      ***_wr_txns.txt & ***_rd_txns.txt                                             *
 *                      (these files have all the perf details & axi attributes)                      *
 *                                                                                                    *
 * plot_perf.py       : This script can parse the generated files and plot perf graph                 *
 *                      Execute "plot_perf_graph" to automatically plot                               *
 *                      (note: this executable requires two .txt files as input args)                 *
 * Example binding    : `include "bind_*_axi_tracker_dut.svh" in hdl_top or tb_top which              *
 *                      connects the tracker with the DUT                                             *
 *                      PARAMETER .LOG1 & .LOG2 can be passed with user-defined names for these files *
 *                                                                                                    *
 *****************************************************************************************************/
